vmware.description: VMware managed object root assignements This module defines the VMware SNMP MIB root and its primary subtrees.

vmwSystem.name: vmwSystem
vmwSystem.description: Parent of all managed objects relating to system software identification.

vmwVirtMachines.name: vmwVirtMachines
vmwVirtMachines.description: Parent of all managed objects relating to virtual machine inventory.

vmwResources.name: vmwResources
vmwResources.description: Parent of all managed objects relating to resource utilization.

vmwProductSpecific.name: vmwProductSpecific
vmwProductSpecific.description: parent of objects specific to a given hardware/software product.

vmwTraps.name: vmwTraps
vmwTraps.description: Managed objects defined under this node are only visible in notifications varbind lists and can not be polled.

vmwSRM.name: vmwSRM
vmwSRM.description: Managed objects defined under this node are only visible in notifications from Site Recovery Manager and can not be polled.

vmwVCHA.name: vmwVCHA
vmwVCHA.description: Managed objects defined under this node are only visible in notifications from VMware Virtual Center High Availability and can not be polled.

vmwVmon.name: vmwVmon
vmwVmon.description: Managed objects defined under this node are for VMware Service Lifecycle Manager.

vmwOID.name: vmwOID
vmwOID.description: Assignments under this are no longer made.

vmwareAgentCapabilities.name: vmwareAgentCapabilities
vmwareAgentCapabilities.description: All agent capabilities defnitions occur under this.

vmwNsxManager.name: vmwNsxManager
vmwNsxManager.description: Objects used by VMware NSX Manager and related components.

vmwNetworkInsight.name: vmwNetworkInsight
vmwNetworkInsight.description: Objects used by VMware vRealize Network Insight and related components.

vmwExperimental.name: vmwExperimental
vmwExperimental.description: Used for product testing and development.

vmwObsolete.name: vmwObsolete
